OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSeattle is first US city to
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fban caste discrimination   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Seattle has become the first US city to
OL,6, ban discrimination based on caste after
OL,7, a vote by the city council.            
OL,9,FCouncilwoman Kshama Sawant, who wrote  
OL,10,Fthe legislation, said the fight against
OL,11,Fcaste bias "is deeply connected to the 
OL,12,Ffight against all forms of oppression".
OL,14,FAdvocates of the ban say that it is    
OL,15,Fneeded to prevent caste bias from      
OL,16,Fbecoming more prevalent in the US.     
OL,18,FThe caste system in India dates back   
OL,19,Fover 3,000 years and divides Hindu     
OL,20,Fsociety into rigid hierarchical groups.
